description:
Lm: Table containing license management (LM) data for Ericsson radio access network cells, including timestamps, cell identifiers, LM state, and license inventory information.
dateTime: Timestamp of data record.
Area_Name: Geographic area of the cell.
CellId: Unique identifier of the cell site.
Id2: Duplicate of CellId.
Id3:  Unclear purpose, likely a redundant identifier (value always '1').
vsDataType:  Data type identifier (always 'vsDataLm').
vsDataFormatVersion: Version of the data format (always 'EricssonSpecificAttributes').
Lm.lastInventoryChange: Timestamp of last license inventory change.
Lm.referenceToLicenseServer: Reference to the license server (appears empty in sample data).
Lm.fingerprint: Unique fingerprint identifying the LM configuration.
Lm.fingerprintUpdateable: Boolean indicating if the fingerprint is updatable.
Lm.lmState: Current state of the license manager (e.g., 'NORMAL').
Lm.lastLicenseInventoryRefresh: Timestamp of last license inventory refresh.
Lm.lmId:  Unclear purpose, likely a redundant identifier (value always '1').
